  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-8">
    <p>
      <%= link_to "Ancestry.com", "http://www.ancestry.com" %> offers access to 14 billion global historical records
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Build your own tree</li>
      <li>Collaborate with others</li>
      <li>Easily search records and documents</li>
      <li>Mobile applications</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Free to LDS members at <%= link_to "https://familysearch.org/partner/ancestry", "https://familysearch.org/partner/ancestry" %></p>
  </div>
</div>

<hr/>

