      <li>Benefit from expertise in British and Irish geneology</li>
      <li>Accurate records, easily searchablements</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Free to LDS members at <%= link_to "https://familysearch.org/partner/findmypast", "https://familysearch.org/partner/findmypast" %></p>
  </div>
</div>

<hr/>

